======================================================================
			      * ZincBB *
======================================================================

An open-source electronic bulletin board written in Erlang, and
powered by the Erlang Web Framework Nitrogen.

ZincBB is made available under the Apache 2.0 license.


======================================================================
Setup
======================================================================

After cloning the repository, dependent libraries must be fetched as
git submodule repostories. 

Dependencies:
git submodule init
git submodule update

Build: 
make

Setup (sets up mnesia schema):
./bootstrap

Run:
./start


======================================================================
Source Format
======================================================================

The erl_tidy library is used to format the zincBB code used in this
project. To apply the tidy, simply type:

./zntools tidy

